bio: BEEF, Marvel’s Thunderbolts, Star Wars: Skeleton Crew. Past: Robot & Frank, Dave, Francis & the Lights, Kendrick, Keem, Haim, Benny Blanco, etc.

social_posts.post_text: @taylour and I doing a little q&a for "We Cry Together" at @indiewire's Short Film Showcase, if you're in the Los Angeles area this Friday, Dec. 9.

A first look at my brilliant friend @beherelater’s BEEF, from @a24 and @netflix, starring @stevenyeun and @aliwong. Coming April 6th. Grateful to have been a director and EP, and work on something that was so special to so many people involved. More soon.
BEEF April 6th @netflix @a24 @beherelater @steveyeun @aliwong beautiful poster design by @doyrivative
null
Beef with those you love. April 6th @netflix @a24 @sxsw (@beherelater styled by the photo drop)
2nd Beef Poster. April 6th @netflix @a24

Some photos from the BEEF premiere last night. Proud of @beherelater and everyone who put so much of themselves into this show. Thanks for being my date @itsbennyblanco April 6th on Netflix 📸 Charley Galway/Getty
BEEF now streaming on @netflix

“Crows love me.” Gonna post some little BTS stuff on here over the next few weeks and try to stay away from spoilers. It took an incredible effort by a ton of people to pull this show off and hopefully that will come through here. Mark Jackson and @markschwag were our crow wranglers. #beef #beefnetflix

Yes, @steveyeun did sing it, live. So grateful to @minjason and everyone from @citizenschurchla who came out and made it real. So many personal connections @beherelater brought together to make the show special (and watch carefully for a @beherelater cameo in Episode 7, sorry I cropped him out the first time) and thanks to @arielrechtshaid and @thehaxancloak for producing the music #beef

Back on set I’d joke with @stevenyeun, @beherelater and @larksss that the action side of our show was like Heat (one of my all-time favorites), but not quite. So I made this little poster during shooting because I’m a nerd. And I left Val Kilmer on because I was very tired. Also a little bonus video of painting the truck while trying channel @aliwong #beef
Trapped in a maze of his own creation, as he would say. Couldn’t be prouder of @beherelater and this amazing project and group of people he put together.  #beef non-iPhone shots by Andrew Cooper

The incomparable @aliwong in some of her most emotional scenes from the show, along with the amazing @joeyunlee and @itskaylablake. The therapy scene in 7 called for just one setup, starting in profile and circling around into a frontal shot, timed to match Amy’s opening up within the scene. Ali nailed it by the third take.  #beef Non-iPhone shots by Andrew Cooper.
Day 1. #beef

@steveyeun & @youngmazino doing their own stunt, with the help of our coordinator Charles Grisham and his great team. And a bonus shot of @graaceyuun sitting in the courtyard that was so important to @beherelater’s story. Grace designed it to be built seamlessly into our existing location. #beef #a24 #netflix #bts

@larksss appreciation post: Starting with a nifty lo-fi headlights rig he and his incredible team designed for night chase work. We were incredibly lucky to have someone able to pull off such artful imagery throughout the show, especially on a TV schedule. #beef
Some film stills I took from the last days of BEEF. @beherelater directing @steveyeun and @aliwong in the first episode he ever directed and last of the season. #beef

As always, grateful to work with such incredible collaborators:  @kendricklamar @davefree @taylour @knucklewood @pglang @parkpictures @thecodeword @jamierabineau and everyone else who made this so special.

Just an incredible group of people that came together to bring @beherelater’s vision to life. Lovely to have so many of them recognized (including the ones on more squares than Instagram will let me post). But there simply wouldn’t be a show at all without all the hard work everyone put in, and very grateful as always for getting to be a part of it.
